source.name: CTA - Ridership - Bus Routes - Monthly Day-Type Averages & Totals
source.description: This dataset shows monthly averages, by day type (weekday, Saturday or Sunday/Holiday) and monthly totals for all CTA bus routes, back to 2001. See attached readme file for information on how these numbers are calculated.
